                     <title xml:lang="he">לקוטים שונים בקבלה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Contains: selected pieces from Sha῾are orah (folios 367v-369r) and Sha῾are tsedeḳ (folios 369r-370r) of Joseph Gikatilla; fragments from Ma῾arekhet ha-elohut (folios 371v-372r); Sefer ha-bahir (folio 372r-373r); Keter shem ṭov of Shem Tov ibn Gaon (folio 373r); gimatri᾿ot (folio 373v). </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
